# demo-mocha-yatt-pipe

A simple demo for reporting Mocha test results with `yatt-pipe`.

## Requirements

-   Node.js >= 18
-   npm (please use npm as the package manager)

## Installation

```bash
npm install
```

## Running Tests

```bash
# Run tests with Mocha
npm run mocha

# Run tests with Mocha and generate JUnit report
npm run mocha-junit
```

